4-inch LED round eyeball recessed gimbal, 15 watts, 900-1400 lumens, available in dim to warm color temperature (CCT), 50,000 hours rated life, white, brushed nickel or black finish, 10 year warranty residential/5 year warranty commercial.

  • Beam Angle: 38° wide beam with 20° tilt and 360° rotation

  • Junction Box Wire Capacity: Max 5 No 12 AWG or 8 No 14 AWG
  • Power Factor: 0.95
  • Approved Location: Insulated Ceiling & Wet Locations
  • IP Rating: IP 54
  • Air Tight: Yes
  • Ambient Temperature: -40°F (-40°C) to +104°F (+40°C)
  • Projected Life: 70% Light Output at 50,000 Hours
  • Certification: cULus, Energy Star (except DTW & 5CCT), T24
  • Warranty: 10 Year Residential / 5 Year Commercial

name: 8Ft. LED 42 Watt Split Version T8 Lamp
description:
8ft. LED split version T8 lamp, 42 watts, 6,000 lumens, available in 4000K or 5000K color temperature (CCT), clear or frosted PC lens, up to 50,000 hours rated life, 5 years warranty.

FEATURES

  • Type B: Ballast Override (AC Direct), Connect One End or Both Ends (Dual Function) - UL No. E342884
  • Split Model (2 Four-Foot Lamps), Snap & Save
  • 5-Year Warranty
  • Glass tube: Better Transparency and Thermal Conductivity than Plastic

ELECTRICAL

  • Voltage: 120-277V; 50/60Hz AC
  • Power Factor: >0.90
  • THD: <20%
  • Wattage: 42W
  • Efficacy: 142 LPW

  • Base Type: FA8 (Single Pin)
  • Glass Tube: Better Transparency and Thermal Conductivity than Plastic
  • Clear Glass
  • 2 Magnetic Mounting Clips per Lamp
  • Ambient Operating Temperature: -13°F to 113°F
  • Rated life: 50,000 hrs
  • IP Rating: IP20 (Indoor)

LIGHTING

  • Dimming: Non Dimmable
  • Total Lumens: 6000LM
  • Color Temperatures: 4000K/5000K
  • Color Rendering Index: CRI ≥ 80
  • Beam Angle: 120°

APPLICATIONS

  • Crystal Glass 8 Foot T8 Tube switches from fluorescent tubes to LED, giving more cost efficiency by providing the same amount of lumen output with less energy consumption. The LED tube offers a soft and bright light distribution.

name: 6-Inch Round LED 15 Watt Regressed Gimbal
description:
6-inch LED round regressed gimbal, 15 watts, 900-1400 lumens, available in dim to warm color temperature (CCT), suitable insulated ceiling for wet locations, 50,000 hours rated life, 10 year residential/5 year commercial.

DESCRIPTION

  • 6" Round Regressed Gimbal Led 15w With Integral Driver In Connection Box Adjustable Yet Air-Tight Without Housing Needed

FEATURES & BENEFITS

  • 3 1/2" Deep - Install Where Ceiling Space is limited 
  • Type IC Rated - No Housing Required
  • Driver Inside Connection Box - No Junction Box Needed
  • Directional Beam - Great for Sloped Ceilings and Artwork
  • CRI 90+ for True Color Rendering
  • Available in single CCT, Dim to Warm 30-20K & 30-18K, & 5CCT

MOUNTING

  • Cut Hole In Ceiling And Snap Fixture In Opening With Attached Spring Clips. Ceiling Clearance Required: 3 1/2"

SPECIFICATION

  • Applications: Sloped Ceilings up to 20°, General Lighting
  • Energy Used: 15W
  • Color Temperature: DTW 30-20
  • Light Output (lm): 900lm, 980lm, 1100lm, 1200lm, 1250lm, 1300lm, 1400lm
  • Beam Angle: 38° wide beam with 20° tilt and 360° rotation
  • CRI: 90 +
  • Default Driver Input: 120V AC Triac Dimmable
  • Optional Driver Input: 120V-347V AC 0-10V Dimmable
  • Junction Box Wire Capacity: Max 5 No 12 AWG or 8 No 14 AWG
  • Power Factor: 0.95
  • Approved Location: Insulated Ceiling & Wet Locations
  • IP Rating: IP 54
  • Air Tight: Yes
  • Ambient Temperature: -40°F (-40°C) to +104°F (+40°C)
  • Projected Life: 70% Light Output at 50,000 Hours
  • Certification: cULus, Energy Star (except DTW & 5CCT), T24
  • Warranty: 10 Year Residential / 5 Year Commercial
